rComments: AWESOME prof, loved her Bioethics class... very fair, approachable and explains things VERY clearly. Has a way of turning dry material into something worth listening to :)Look forward to future classes with her.
One of the best lecturers. She's extremely clear and insightful. I would recommend taking any class she teaches. She's also extremely sexy.

This is my 4th course with Prof. Panitch.  Extremely intelligent, approachable, articulate and fair.  Possess great empathy for her students.  I only hope I will be fortunate enought to participate in another of her classes at some future date.
Amazing prof.  Interesting, funny, and obviously very intelligent.  Would definitely take another course with her.
Such a good professor. So helpful, knowledgeable and clear. Interesting subject matter. Great class.
